A '''gimer bush''' was a [[Plant/Legends|plant]] that grew in the [[Mountain/Legends|mountains]] on [[Genesia]]. A [[Gimer stick/Legends|cane]] used by [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] was constructed from gimer. He often chewed on the stick to consume its helpful nutrients, which also aided him in meditation. The bush also grew on [[Ohma-D'un/Legends|Ohma-D'un]] and was known for its sap which could be made into a juice. The bush was also found on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] and [[Dagobah/Legends|Dagobah]].

